[While Chios, a Greek territory, is an island adjacent to the western
Turkish coast, Evros is a mainland Greek territory, the northernmost
province of Greece, bordering the European (Thrace) part of Turkey; for a
map showing both, see
<http://www.greektravel.com/maps/map1.jpg>.
An official notification with epidemiological and laboratory-confirmatory
data, including the species involved, is urgently anticipated. - Mod.AS]
